## API Reference

### Correct CameraFocusOptions

```typescript
{
  targetFill?: number;  // NOT 'scale'
  blendStyle?: "gentle" | "snappy" | "stiff";
  autoReset?: boolean;
}
```

### Correct CameraShakeOptions

```typescript
{
  intensity?: number;  // NOT 'intensityX' or 'intensityY'
  frequency?: number;
}
```

### Correct CameraResetOptions

```typescript
{
  blendStyle?: "gentle" | "snappy" | "stiff";  // NOT 'duration'
}
```

### Correct dutchTilt signature

```typescript
dutchTilt(angle: number): void  // NOT dutchTilt({ angle, duration, spring })
```

### Correct CameraFlashOptions

```typescript
{
  intensity?: number;
  color?: string;
  // NO 'duration' property
}
```

